import { Stack, TextContainer, Button } from "@shopify/polaris"
const AddEmail = () => {
    return (
        <Stack>
            <Stack.Item fill>
                <TextContainer>contact@emailmywebhooks.com</TextContainer>
            </Stack.Item>
            <Stack.Item>
                <Button plain destructive>Delete</Button>
            </Stack.Item>
        </Stack>
    )
}

export default AddEmail
